short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Secure your group with the My Legacy Life Community builder app providing personal LinkedIn members private, spam-free, networking.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The My Legacy Life Community allows the members in the community to connect with each other, with the knowledge we are like-minded in creating purpose driven results connected to living a Legacy Life. Trusted LinkedIn members can connect in a private, invitation only community, offering message integrity, security, no spamming or bots and trusted referrals. We encourage networking in the group and offer this app as a dedicated and secure community for business and personal networking. 
When you align your divine message to your purpose-driven goals you can Reach Millions and Live a Legacy life of your dreams.
